body_html:
Go to /tmp, where is all the way outside of your directory. There you could find cifar10_train and cifar10_data folders. Inside cifar10_data folder, damaged cifar-10-binary.tar.gz file is located. The cifar10_train.py keep recognize this damaged file as intact one, error message keep shown.
Therefore you should remove the cifar10_train and cifar10_data folders and re-python cifar10_train.py.

body:
Go to /tmp, where is all the way outside of your directory. There you could find cifar10_train and cifar10_data folders. Inside cifar10_data folder, damaged cifar-10-binary.tar.gz file is located. The cifar10_train.py keep recognize this damaged file as intact one, error message keep shown. 
Therefore you should remove the cifar10_train and cifar10_data folders and re-python cifar10_train.py.
